Object Flight Path: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
Summary: Dissapearing light moving at high speeds
divs: Sighting DetailsI was on the road headed to check livestock when I thought was an airplane heading west all of a sudden turned and quickly went east and stopped then moved back to the west and then to the east and stopped. I called my dad and told him to look to the north he opened the door and immediately the object vanished. Looked like it shot straight up. The sky was clear, so it couldn't go behind clouds.
